    "id": "106",
    "filename": "106-from-please-hold-to-how-can-i-help-you-the-voice-shift.md",
    "title": "From 'Please Hold' to 'How Can I Help You?': The Voice Shift",
    "author": "Sai Chaitanya",
    "role": "Co-founder & Product",
